    "name": "Birdy's Island",
    "steam_appid": 3083760,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌴 <strong>鸟儿的岛屿——独一无二的冒险！</strong> 🐦</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎来到鸟儿的岛屿，在这里你可以体验鸟儿的生活，探索、保护，并享受天空的自由。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083760/extras/d570b50e43160440745fd272da341946.poster.avif?t=1732470966\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083760/extras/d570b50e43160440745fd272da341946.webm?t=1732470966\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083760/extras/d570b50e43160440745fd272da341946.mp4?t=1732470966\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🛡️ <strong>保护你的领地</strong> 🚫</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >人类开始入侵岛屿，威胁它的自然美景。作为一只鸟，你有责任以独特的方式保护你的家园。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083760/extras/7aca2fa22bac1411c54854f19d95d7f6.poster.avif?t=1732470966\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083760/extras/7aca2fa22bac1411c54854f19d95d7f6.webm?t=1732470966\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083760/extras/7aca2fa22bac1411c54854f19d95d7f6.mp4?t=1732470966\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌤️ <strong>翱翔天际</strong> 🌅</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验飞翔的刺激，感受风拂过羽翼的感觉，从高处探索这座岛屿。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083760/extras/73e05a5c91f0efe8fa9cb69146273fa1.poster.avif?t=1732470966\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083760/extras/73e05a5c91f0efe8fa9cb69146273fa1.webm?t=1732470966\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083760/extras/73e05a5c91f0efe8fa9cb69146273fa1.mp4?t=1732470966\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌊 <strong>潜水与游泳</strong> 🐟</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >鸟儿的岛屿不仅仅是飞翔。潜入清澈的水中，探索你的家园的水下美景。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083760/extras/4a0eaa240bb1a26d8ab06b93904781e1.poster.avif?t=1732470966\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083760/extras/4a0eaa240bb1a26d8ab06b93904781e1.webm?t=1732470966\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083760/extras/4a0eaa240bb1a26d8ab06b93904781e1.mp4?t=1732470966\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌱 <strong>呵护环境</strong> 🌳</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过种树来展示你对自然的承诺。你的行动帮助岛屿恢复绿色生机。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083760/extras/945ea597cbfd6861d30cf1e33d69b2db.poster.avif?t=1732470966\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083760/extras/945ea597cbfd6861d30cf1e33d69b2db.webm?t=1732470966\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083760/extras/945ea597cbfd6861d30cf1e33d69b2db.mp4?t=1732470966\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🚮 <strong>见证污染的影响</strong> 🌍</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >亲眼目睹人类造成的破坏，参观曾经洁净的海滩，如今已布满污染。这是每只鸟的行动号召。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083760/extras/6e7564e9665e0a7e36917f193a03f386.poster.avif?t=1732470966\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083760/extras/6e7564e9665e0a7e36917f193a03f386.webm?t=1732470966\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083760/extras/6e7564e9665e0a7e36917f193a03f386.mp4?t=1732470966\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌳 <strong>在大自然中寻找宁静</strong> 🌸</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在战斗与挑战之间，漫步公园，找到宁静的时刻，提醒你为何而战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083760/extras/ae150b1529d2e8c146da8ff348715d74.poster.avif?t=1732470966\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083760/extras/ae150b1529d2e8c146da8ff348715d74.webm?t=1732470966\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083760/extras/ae150b1529d2e8c146da8ff348715d74.mp4?t=1732470966\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
